🌐 𝗔𝗺𝗮𝘇𝗼𝗻 𝗪𝗼𝗪 🌐

With an objective to help women students build long-term career in technology, Amazon WoW is yet again back this 2022. 

📌 𝗕𝗲𝗻𝗲𝗳𝗶𝘁𝘀:
Amazon WoW will host sessions on tech and leadership development through the year. This would include preparatory sessions for interviews, what to expect during technical online assessment, how to write a good resume, how to choose a career path, opportunity to apply for roles at Amazon, and more.

🎯 𝗘𝗹𝗶𝗴𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆 𝗖𝗿𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗮:
✅ Amazon WoW is open to all women students across engineering campuses in India.
✅ Any women student who is currently pursuing a four-year B.Tech/BE or two-year MCA, M.Tech/ME program or five year Dual Degree can participate.

❓ 𝗛𝗼𝘄 𝗶𝘀 𝗔𝗺𝗮𝘇𝗼𝗻 𝗪𝗼𝗪 𝘀𝘁𝗿𝘂𝗰𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲𝗱?
👉 Interested women students are required to register on the portal.
👉 The Amazon WoW program aims to engage and connect with registered participants on an ongoing basis. The events will be conducted virtually and the list of events for every quarter will be published in the events section.
👉 Each session will have limited number of slots and will be filled through RSVP. Participants will have to register for each session to be part of the live session. They will also have access to recordings of the session post completion of each session.

𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗿 𝗡𝗼𝘄!
